00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.424
<b>Using Safety In Motion® helps you protect your body.</b>

00:00:03.648 --> 00:00:06.400
<b>However, protecting your spine is critical.</b>

00:00:06.688 --> 00:00:10.240
<b>Back pain can affect almost every activity you do.</b>

00:00:10.976 --> 00:00:14.528
<b>You've learned that your risk is high </b>
<b>if you're reaching into your red zone.</b>

00:00:15.168 --> 00:00:18.240
<b>But the risk is even higher if your heels are off the ground</b>

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.736
<b>and there is a load or tool in your hand.</b>

00:00:21.376 --> 00:00:24.064
<b>Is you see or expereince this, stop and think, </b>

00:00:24.192 --> 00:00:25.984
<b>"How can I do this a better way?"</b>

00:00:26.496 --> 00:00:30.460
<b>Remember, positioning your elbows just six inches closer to your side </b>

00:00:30.461 --> 00:00:33.060
<b>can cut the force in half every time you lift,</b>

00:00:33.152 --> 00:00:34.784
<b>carry, push, or pull.</b>

